
From the following table, write a SQL query to find the details of all employees whose last name is ‘Dosni’ or ‘Mardy’. Return emp_idno, emp_fname, emp_lname, and emp_dept.Programming

Sample table : emp_details

 EMP_IDNO EMP_FNAME       EMP_LNAME         EMP_DEPT
